Package: gpxui
Title: Read and Show GPX Files
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mihai", "Valcu", , "Mihai.Valcu@bi.mpg.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6907-7802"))
Description: Read and display waypoints and tracks from GPX files in a given directory. When the directory is on a Garmin GPS some info regarding the GPS is retrieved as well.
